              Together, they form the foundation of creating digital products that are not only visually appealing
              but also intuitive, functional, and enjoyable to use.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
              <strong>User Experience (UX) Design</strong> focuses on the overall feel and functionality of a product.
