              smooth and meaningful. UX designers map user journeys, create wireframes, and ensure every touchpoint
              serves a purpose in helping users achieve their goals efficiently.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
              <strong>User Interface (UI) Design</strong> deals with the visual and interactive elements users engage with.
